title: $ETH: Crypto Exchange KuCoin Burned Millions of Ethereum in Mysterious Event
description: In September 2021, thousands of deposit addresses from popular cryptocurrency exchange KuCoin sent tens of millions of dollars’ worth of Ethereum’s native token $ETH to a burn address, also known as a null address, for unclear reasons.
